OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777680175
OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FSuleiman is also charged with the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a third man, long-
OL,8,Ftime friend Ishmail Hussein, earlier
OL,9,Fthe same day in Southwark, south
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FIn a statement on Thursday, the PM
OL,13,Fbacked the prosecution of people
OL,14,Fchanting "globalise the intifada"
OL,15,Fduring protests, while the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police is reviewing
OL,17,Fwhether future marches can go ahead.
OL,19,FBut how far could a potential ban go,
OL,20,Fand what does the law say currently?
OL,26,@vD@JOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
