OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FWhy is a ban being called for?
OL,8,FAfter Wednesday's antisemitic attack,
OL,9,Fsome have linked a rise in these
OL,10,Fincidents to repeated pro-Palestine
OL,11,Fmarches and recent demonstrations
OL,12,Fvoicing support for Palestine Action,
OL,13,Fa group proscribed as a terror
OL,14,Forganisation by the UK government in
OL,15,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
