OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FSpeaking on Friday morning, Home
OL,7,FOffice Minister Alex Davies-Jones said
OL,8,Fthe government would ban protests if
OL,9,Fnecessary, adding to ITV's Good
OL,10,FMorning Britain, that anyone
OL,11,Fconsidering attending a demonstration
OL,12,Fshould "check themselves".
OL,14,FShe said: "Look at what they're doing,
OL,15,Flook at who you're standing next to
OL,16,Fand what is being said, what they're
OL,17,Fwearing.
OL,26,@tD@HOUtD@YO]vD@KOU
