OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,F"Because this is a responsibility on
OL,7,Fall of us to prevent the rise in
OL,8,Fdivision and hatred that we're seeing
OL,9,Fin our country, and to prevent anyone
OL,10,Ffrom feeling unsafe, intimidated or
OL,11,Falarmed."
OL,13,FAt a protest outside Downing Street
OL,14,Forganised by Campaign Against
OL,15,FAntisemitism on Thursday evening,
OL,16,Fseveral individuals told ITV News they
OL,17,Fblamed pro-Palestine marches for a
OL,18,Frise in antisemitic incidents.
