OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FTerror watchdog Jonathan Hall has also
OL,7,Fcalled for a moratorium on the marches
OL,8,Ffollowing the stabbing of two Jewish
OL,9,Fmen in Golders Green on Wednesday,
OL,10,Fsaying they had "incubated"
OL,11,Fantisemitism.
OL,13,FThe government are currently appealing
OL,14,Fa court decision which overturned its
OL,15,Fproscription of Palestine Action, with
OL,16,Fa decision in writing expected at a
OL,17,Flater date.
OL,19,FWhat does the law say currently?
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
