OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FOn top of this, in October 2025, the
OL,7,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,8,Fannounced the power to restrict
OL,9,F"repeat" protests taking place for the
OL,10,Fsame reason and in the same location.
OL,12,FIn March 2026, Mahmood approved a
OL,13,Fpolice request to ban an annual pro-
OL,14,FPalestine al-Quds Day march.
OL,16,FThis was the first time a march had
OL,17,Fbeen banned since 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
