OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCould we see a full ban?
OL,13,FThe right to protest in the UK is
OL,14,Fprotected under Article 10 and Article
OL,15,F11 of the Human Rights Act, which
OL,16,Fenshrine freedom of expression, and
OL,17,Ffreedom of assembly and association in
OL,18,Flaw.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
