OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FGoing further than laws currently
OL,7,Fallow would require primary
OL,8,Flegislation when parliament returns
OL,9,Fafter the local elections.
OL,11,FHuman rights groups like Amnesty
OL,12,FInternational have called on people to
OL,13,F"resist those who want power without
OL,14,Faccountability".
OL,16,FIt highlights that so far police have
OL,17,Farrested around 2,700 people
OL,18,Fpeacefully protesting the proscription
OL,19,Fof Palestine Action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
