OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,F"This is dystopian - and unlawful,"
OL,7,Fclaims the campaign group.
OL,9,FIn December 2025, the government
OL,10,Flaunched a review of the current
OL,11,Flegislation governing protests in the
OL,12,FUK to ensure it is "fit for purpose"
OL,13,Fin today's world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
