OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FAsked whether he thought a ban or
OL,7,Ftighter restrictions should be
OL,8,Fenforced, Met Police Commissioner Sir
OL,9,FMark Rowley said it was a matter for
OL,10,Fparliament, but added: "I think the
OL,11,Fhome secretary is right, the law needs
OL,12,Fto be improved," adding that he looked
OL,13,Fforward to the results of the review
OL,14,Finto protest powers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
