OL,3,CWill some protests be banned? Home
OL,4,Csecretary exploring options
OL,6,FAsked about specific phrases viewed by
OL,7,Fsome as antisemitic or inciteful and
OL,8,Foften seen at protests on placards,
OL,9,FRowley said: "I think we should push
OL,10,Fthe boundaries of the law more,"
OL,11,Freferencing the current lack of
OL,12,Fprosecutions for displaying such
OL,13,Fmessages.
OL,15,FFurther marches are planned this
OL,16,Fmonth, with a pro-Palestine march
OL,17,Fscheduled the same day as a far-right
OL,18,FTommy Robinson protest on May 16.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
